text: Authentic home cooked feel of handmade Mian Fen Guo & You Mian.  Lots of ingredients too.  To issue to look for seats as well, highly recommended.
The homemade noodles are delicious and reasonably priced, though,  might need to wait a bit longer. The shop is open daily until 6 PM.‚Äù

I used to eat this when it was the old uncle and auntie and now the young chaps took over.  They have done very well! Compared to the final days of uncle and auntie, the young chap stall soup is more natural and homely and less MSG.  And also faster turnaround!

Have been eating since old uncle times. When these young chaps took over, I was a little skeptical. But they managed to capture the essence of the goodness of the mee Hoon kueh with room for improvement. Definitely my go to for comfort food!
Love this MHK shop, the owner is damn nice, very nostalgic taste. This is my regular go to
